Equation:
\[
N(t) = \frac{K}{1 + \left(\frac{K - N_0}{N_0}\right) \cdot e^{-r \cdot A(t) \cdot t}}, \quad \text{with } A(t) = \frac{1}{1 + e^{-k(t - t_0)}}
